## ğŸš€ Cara Instalasi

### Step 1: Copy File HTML
Salin semua file HTML baru ke folder root project Anda:
- `user-home.html`
- `user-login.html`
- `user-register.html`
- `user-products.html`
- `user-product-detail.html`
- `user-cart.html`
- `user-profile.html`

### Step 2: Copy File JavaScript
Salin file JavaScript ke folder `assets/js/`:
- `user-auth.js`
- `user-cart.js`

### Step 3: Verifikasi Firebase Config
Pastikan file `assets/js/firebase-config.js` sudah ada dan terisi dengan benar:

```javascript
// firebase-config.js
import { initializeApp } from 'https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.7.1/firebase-app.js';
import { getAuth } from 'https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.7.1/firebase-auth.js';
import { getFirestore } from 'https://www.gstatic.com/firebasejs/10.7.1/firebase-firestore.js';

const firebaseConfig = {
    apiKey: "YOUR_API_KEY",
    authDomain: "YOUR_AUTH_DOMAIN",
    projectId: "YOUR_PROJECT_ID",
    storageBucket: "YOUR_STORAGE_BUCKET",
    messagingSenderId: "YOUR_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID",
    appId: "YOUR_APP_ID"
};

const app = initializeApp(firebaseConfig);
export const auth = getAuth(app);
export const db = getFirestore(app);
```

### Step 4: Setup Firebase Firestore

Buat collections berikut di Firebase Firestore:

1. **Collection: `products`**
   ```javascript
   {
       name: "Hijab Segi Empat Premium",
       price: 150000,
       category: "segi-empat",
       stock: 100,
       description: "Hijab berkualitas premium...",
       material: "Voal Premium",
       size: "110 x 110 cm",
       createdAt: "2025-11-26"
   }
   ```

2. **Collection: `users`**
   ```javascript
   {
       name: "Nama User",
       email: "user@email.com",
       phone: "08123456789",
       role: "user",
       createdAt: "2025-11-26",
       address: []
   }
   ```

3. **Collection: `orders`** (optional)
   ```javascript
   {
       userId: "user_uid",
       items: [...],
       total: 150000,
       status: "pending",
       createdAt: "2025-11-26"
   }
   ```

### Step 5: Test Website
1. Buka VS Code
2. Klik kanan pada `user-home.html`
3. Pilih "Open with Live Server"
4. Website akan terbuka di browser

