## ğŸ¨ Customization

### Mengubah Warna Theme:
Edit gradient di setiap file HTML:

```css
/* Ganti gradient utama */
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);

/* Dengan warna pilihan Anda */
background: linear-gradient(135deg, #WARNA1 0%, #WARNA2 100%);
```

### Menambah Kategori:
Edit di `user-home.html` dan `user-products.html`:

```html
<div class="category-card" onclick="filterCategory('kategori-baru')">
    <div class="category-icon">ğŸ€</div>
    <h3>Kategori Baru</h3>
</div>
```

### Menambah Kode Promo:
Edit di `user-cart.js`:

```javascript
const PROMO_CODES = {
    'HIJAB10': { discount: 10000, type: 'fixed', minPurchase: 100000 },
    'KODEBARU': { discount: 25000, type: 'fixed', minPurchase: 150000 }
};
```

